quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,"∆Āeyngu laam…óo on jokkitii o wi'i: Mi la…ď…ďinaa hoore-am e faandanagol bone, mi faandoraaki …óum kadi la…ď…ďingol hoore-am; sabu wonkii ne…ó…óanke ko heewuki yamirde bone, tawde ki oo√Īoray e ko welataki, yiltugol ki e …óum sa…óta, si wanaa kin ki Alla yurmaa, O da…ónda ki e yamirgol bone. Pellet Joomi am ko Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Hinnotoo…óo …ďe."
  12,54,"Nde laa…ďugol Yuusufa ngol e ganndal makko fee√Īunoo, laam…óo on wi'ani golloowo mun …ďen: Addanee lam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am. ∆Āe addi mo. Nde o yewtunoo mo, ganndal oya ngal e haqqille makko …óen …ďanngani mo, o wi'ani mo: An on Yuusufa, a wonii hannde ka amen, jom-nokku e jaahu, hoolaa…óo."
  12,55,"Annabi Yuusufa maaki: "Halfinam reenugol ngaluuji jawle …óen e √Īaameteeji leydi Misra ndin, min ko mi reenoowo hoolnii…óo, anndu…óo ko mi wa…óata."
  12,56,"Ko wano Men neeminirnoo non e Yuusufa la…ď…ďingol mo …ďoortindira mo e kaso, Men neeminiri e makko √Īimnugol ka leydi Misra, himo jippoo ho…óa e mayri nokku kala ka o yi…ói. Me…óen ye…óa yurmeendeAa Amen nden aduna on mo Men muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Amen …ďen. Men yeebataa njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen, ko Men timminiroo…ďe ndi ko aldaa e …óuytugol."
  12,57,"Pellet ko mbarjaari ndi Alla hebili ndin laakara …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude diini njo…ďdi aduna ndin, wonannde …ďen gom…óim…ďe Alla …ďe laatii huliroo…ďe Mo …óoftagol yamirooje Makko wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko."
  12,58,"Baaba-gootoo…ďe Yuusufa …ďen ardiri Misra e ko yeeyetee, …ďe naati ka makko. O anndi ko baaba-gootoo…ďe makko …ďen nii, kono kam…ďe …ďe annditaali mo; tawde dumunna on juutii kadi mbaadi makko ndin waylike, hari ko o cukalel fewno ko …ďe buginoo mo ka woyndu."
  12,59,"Tuma o jonnunoo…ďe ko …ďe lanndii kon e gabbe e njoo…ďa, …ďe humpiti mo wonnde hi…ďe mari musi…ó…óo baaba-gootoojo mo …ďe acci ka ben mun, o maakani …ďe: addanee lam musi…ó…óo mon baaba-gooto, mi …ďeydana on ko ngelooba ronndoo. E on yi'aali wonnde mi…óo timmina …ďetu ngun Mi alaa e …óuytude, e wonnde ko mi mo∆ī∆īo weernoo…ďe …ďen?"
  12,60,"Si on addanaali lam mo, haray fenaande mon nden …ďanngii wiide hi…óon mari musi…ó…óo baaba-gooto. Mi …ďetitantaa on √Īaametee, wata on …ďado kadi leydi am ndin."
  12,61,"Baaba-gootoo…ďe makko …ďen jaabii mo: Men …óa…ď…ďiray mo ben makko, men etoo fii mun. Menen ko men golloo…ďe kon ko yamir-…óaa men ko aldaa e ra…ď…ďindinagol."
  12,62,"Yuusufu maakani golloo…ďe makko …ďen: Jonnitee …ďee doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óen fii no …ďe annditiroya tuma ruttii ka yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe wonnde e soondanaano …ďe, …óum wa…óay …ďe yiltioo hara ontuma hi…ďe wonndi e musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on. ∆äum ko fii no …ďe tabintirina Yuusufa goonga ma…ď…ďe kan, o ja…ďana …ďe doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  12,63,"Tuma nde …ďe ruttinoo ka ben ma…ď…ďe, …ďe fillanii mo ko Yuusufa teddini …ďe kon, …ďe wi'i: Ko an yo …ďen amen, men salante …ďetu si men yahdaali e musi…ó…óo amen on, immindin mo e amen. Si a immindinii men, men …ďetante. Men fodii ma reenugol mo ruttoda e makko himo hisi."